OL,7,FFor many thousands of families this
OL,8,FChristmas, simply turning on the lights
OL,9,Fand the heating is an expense they
OL,10,Fcannot afford.
OL,12,FThey will be making decisions not about
OL,13,Fwhether to have another mince pie and
OL,14,Fwatch the new King's first festive
OL,15,Fbroadcast, but whether they can afford
OL,16,Fto avoid sitting in the cold and dark.
OL,18,FWe are in the middle of a cost of
OL,19,Fliving crisis on a scale rarely seen,
OL,20,Fwith too many people struggling with
OL,21,Fthe very basics of modern life.
OL,3,CSpare a thought for families on
OL,4,Cprepayment meters who may have to spend
OL,5,CChristmas in the dark
